{
  "id": "adv_love_2505_05_04",
  "title": "Episode 5 Part 4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分の想いを、チサに伝えた\nそれを聞き、チサの出した答えは――"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs006.wav",
      "text": "………………ごめんなさい\n私、やっぱり、そんなに強くなれない……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs007.wav",
      "text": "サキュバスとして生きても\n人間として生きても\n二人なら幸せかもしれない"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs008.wav",
      "text": "でも……っ、きっと、長くは続かないから\n私は、サキュバスでも、人間でもないし\nきっと悲しいことになっちゃうと思うから"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs009.wav",
      "text": "だから……\n私のことは忘れて、幸せになって下さい"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "チサの体が輝き始めた……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-ngs003.wav",
      "text": "え……何、あれ……\n攻撃……ううん、もっと、温かい……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs010.wav",
      "text": "これは、お母さんから習った特別な魔術……\n私の半分を、人間としての生命エネルギーを\n使えば、一度くらいは使えるはずだから"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "チサ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-chs011.wav",
      "text": "短い間だったけど\n大切な思い出をありがとう\nいつか、もっと強くなれたら、その時は――"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事情により、妹のすみれと一緒に\n祖父母の家に住むようになって一年……\n平凡な僕は、ありふれた日々を過ごしていた"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "変わったことといえば……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-smr003.wav",
      "text": "お兄ちゃーん、明日のことなんだけど……\n……あれ、どうしたの、ぼーっとして\nまた、なんかむずむずしてる感じ？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "変わったことといえば……\n一年ほど前の記憶に\nぼんやりとしたところがあるくらいだろうか"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-smr004.wav",
      "text": "お医者さんも言ってたでしょ？\n無理して思い出そうとすることない、って\nだから、ほら……考えないようにしよう？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://api.diveidolypapi.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_04/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_02-smr005.wav",
      "text": "その期間、何してたのかは分かんないけど\nまぁ、今は元気なんだから大丈夫だよ！\nじゃあ、戸締まりちゃんとしてね？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何か、大切なことを忘れている\nそんな気がするが……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "表で何か、凄い音がした"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "扉を開けてみよう"
    }
  ]
}